title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Everything goes smoothly for you today if you take time to create a manageable schedule. You likely feel in control, highly capable, and creative. Others call on you for your skills and common sense. Your stamina and perseverance are strong. But if some aspect of your life or someone elses jumps off the rails now, youre tempted to stubbornly continue on your path without acknowledging the immediate crisis. But the whims of fate do not always conform to your preconceived terms and rigid timetable. Use your confidence and commitment to manage the current circumstances like a boss. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
